msgid ""
"This is a toggle option which controls the Loop Playlist setting. If Loop "
"Playlist is enabled, then &juk; will start playing from the beginning when "
"it has finished playing every song in the current playlist."
msgstr ""
"Dette er et valg der kontrollerer indstillingen for afspilning i løkke. Hvis "
